SampleStandardDeviation - Class in com.github.jessemull.microflexbiginteger.stat
This class calculates the sample standard deviation of big integer plate stacks, plates, wells and well sets as the square root of the unbiased sample variance.
SampleStandardDeviation() - Constructor for class com.github.jessemull.microflexbiginteger.stat.SampleStandardDeviation
 
SampleVariance - Class in com.github.jessemull.microflexbiginteger.stat
This class calculates the sample variance of BigInteger plate stacks, plates, wells and well sets as the sum of the second moment divided by the number of values less one.
SampleVariance() - Constructor for class com.github.jessemull.microflexbiginteger.stat.SampleVariance

Skewness - Class in com.github.jessemull.microflexbiginteger.stat
This class calculates the skewness of BigInteger plate stacks, plates, wells and well sets using the following unbiased formula:

[n / (n - 1) * (n - 2)] * SUMOF(Third Moment / (Standard Deviation)^3) where n is the number of values

Statistical operations can be performed on stacks, plates, sets and wells using standard or aggregated functions.
